#: front-page.php:26
msgid "Built for Hawaii"
msgstr "Fausia mo Hawaiʻi"

#: front-page.php:33
msgid "Civic Engagement Tools"
msgstr "Meafaigaluega Auaunaga Faitulafono"

#: front-page.php:33
msgid "for the People of Hawaii"
msgstr "mo Tagata o Hawaiʻi"

#: front-page.php:43
msgid "Government information shouldn't require a law degree to navigate. Civi.Me makes it simple to stay informed, show up, and have your voice heard — in plain language, for free."
msgstr "E le tatau ona manaʻomia se tikeri tulafono e malamalama ai i faʻamatalaga o le malo. Faia e Civi.Me e faigofie ai ona tumau iloa, agai atu, ma faalogoina lou leo — i upu māmā, fua."

#: front-page.php:53
msgid "What matters to you?"
msgstr "O le a le mea tāua iā te oe?"

#: front-page.php:56
msgid "Browse meetings"
msgstr "Suesue fonotaga"

#: front-page.php:167
msgid "The challenge"
msgstr "Le luʻitau"

#: front-page.php:169
msgid "Civic participation should be accessible for all residents"
msgstr "E tatau ona avanoa le auai faitulafono mo tagata uma o le nuu"

#: front-page.php:172
msgid "People want to be engaged, but the barriers make it feel impossible. We're removing them."
msgstr "E manaʻo tagata e auai, ae faia e puipuiga e foliga mai e le mafai. Tatou te aveese i latou."

#: front-page.php:190
msgid "Buried information"
msgstr "Faʻamatalaga natia"

#: front-page.php:191
msgid "Meeting agendas are buried in PDFs across dozens of county and state websites with no consistent format."
msgstr "Ua natia polokalame fonotaga i totonu o PDF i luga o itulau taaloga o le itumalo ma le setete e leai se faiga tutusa."

#: front-page.php:203
msgid "No timely alerts"
msgstr "Leai ni laʻasaga taimi talafeagai"

#: front-page.php:204
msgid "Residents find out about decisions that affect their neighborhoods after the fact — if at all."
msgstr "E iloa e tagata o le nuu ni faaiuga e aʻafia ai o latou nu'u ina ua uma ona faia — pe afai e iloa lava."

#: front-page.php:219
msgid "Bureaucratic language"
msgstr "Gagana faʻavae"

#: front-page.php:220
msgid "Government documents are written for lawyers, not residents. Plain-language summaries are rare."
msgstr "Ua tusia pepa o le malo mo loia, ae le o tagata o le nuu. E seasea ni aotelega gagana māmā."

#: front-page.php:234
msgid "Who are my representatives?"
msgstr "O ai oʻu sui?"

#: front-page.php:235
msgid "Most residents can't name their city council member, let alone their neighborhood board chair."
msgstr "E le mafai e le toʻatele o tagata ona ta'u le igoa o lo latou sui o le fono o le aai, faapefea foi le taitai o le potu."

#: front-page.php:254
msgid "Start here"
msgstr "Amata iinei"

#: front-page.php:256
msgid "Tell us what matters to you"
msgstr "Taʻu mai ia i matou le mea tāua iā te oe"

#: front-page.php:259
msgid "Pick the topics you care about — environment, housing, education, health — and we'll show you the government meetings and councils that handle those issues."
msgstr "Filifili autu e te fiafia i ai — siosiomaga, fale, aʻoaʻoga, soifua maloloina — ma o le a faʻaalia atu ai i latou fonotaga o le malo ma fono e faia ai mea nei."

